Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,陰陽師眼中的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗 不知道你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.88,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,算不算是實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我…終於
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.95,0:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,加快速度 雪風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就可以了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.40,0:02:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,裝甲鬼兵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,無法接近祭壇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,總之先降落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 我們往上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 你也該給我清醒清醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.31,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,命是我的 我愛怎麼用是我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定會讓哥哥復活的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那是不可能的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不 根本就不應該去嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,靈魂之術之所以被嚴禁…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,究其原因是人類根本就不應該去涉足那個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為那個咒法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.65,0:04:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是在人們對超越理解範圍的東西心存敬畏的時代裡煉成的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,現在活在當世的人不可以魯莽地去照貓畫虎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可以祭奠「泰山府君祭」的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,復活該儀式的都唯獨你土御門一家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,難道只許州官放火不許百姓點燈?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,雪風 往下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 快停下 他們是打算前後夾擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這把劍真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是「護身劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,此劍可是經過特別鍛造 而且是年代久遠的靈劍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是剛才那一下讓刀刃缺了一角了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,誒 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不過…不過就磕掉那麼一丁點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,現在情況緊急 就算是弄折了也是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 你也來迎戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,現在別跟我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到你居然不擅長實戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 祭祀儀式要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.59,0:05:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,雪風
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 北斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗?這是北斗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 這條龍是?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.29,0:06:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它是我的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,受歷代當家驅使的使役式 是土御門家的守護聖獸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.84,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}使役式：鬼神、靈獸等以靈體形式存在的古式式神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是為數不多的真龍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你倒是早把它叫出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒法完全駕馭它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 這傢伙沒什麼緊張感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,北斗 我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,去打倒敵人的式神!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.49,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,快跳過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你別強人所難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目 我聽到了 你快放手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我抱得死死的幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這把「護身劍」能用來攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,把劍拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,南麼 三曼多 勃馱喃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(498,660)}namah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}samanta
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(762,660)}buddhanam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,印捺羅也 莎訶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(590,660)}indrah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(732,660)}svaha
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:14.71,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32}註釋:梵語，帝釋天（梵名Sakra,Devanam-indra）真言。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.40,0:08:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,「護身劍」解封後 帝釋天的力量就會消散
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.74,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,變成「破敵劍」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 把那張弓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,箭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這是帶咒力的桃木弓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,應該可以牽制敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒 我來製造機會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,總之一定要阻止儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,知 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.98,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你可是我的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要聽我的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我們上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.73,0:09:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.17,0:10:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 結界解開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.64,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我們出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,又復活了?它要過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.41,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因為它可不是一般厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好勒 我們要去阻止儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.64,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太小瞧我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咒符…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,弄不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多符咒全都是用自己的血寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.60,0:11:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,陰陽師 大連寺鈴鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,謹請泰山府君及冥界諸神…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目…這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…這種東西根本就不是神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴…鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 哥哥!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,…還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,鈴鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我為你製作了新的朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,還不夠啊 鈴鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等…等一下 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,會…給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.21,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的命…會給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,一會兒就好 請再和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是殺死了北斗的仇敵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,活該
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.88,0:14:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託…了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可…惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你這…臭小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,燒盡邪符 「急急如律令」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(735,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.23,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,給我住手 你這臭小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,靈脈?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.46,0:15:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就是這傢伙 暗中作祟的就是它!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,混…蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 土御門家的血脈喲!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 您的心意依然不變嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我會永遠等下去的 無論幾度風雨滄桑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我是你的式神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夜光大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,鍐 哞 怛落 紇里 惡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(488,660)}vam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(545,660)}hu^m
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(620,660)}tra^h
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(718,660)}hri^h
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(793,660)}ah
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,五行連環 「急急如律令」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(733,660)}Order
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不能抬頭看!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只要看了一眼就會被攝走魂魄的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.92,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.00,0:16:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好像結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雪風 已經不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,趕快殺掉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是為那個女人報仇還是什麼別的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在說那種話之前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你還是…先送你哥哥一程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,已經結束了 北斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那個式符
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.89,0:17:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,難道能夠修復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 已經完全失去靈氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但是被春虎稱為北斗的那位應該還健在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這個式神是操作型的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說 通過作為「北斗」的「她」與春虎接觸的施法者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.08,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,現在還在哪裡生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼 是誰那麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這個我想 春虎你應該比我更清楚才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我?我就連她是式神的事都不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我騙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,還一直把你蒙在鼓裡 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天還會再和她相見的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這次可真是鬧得好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 北斗那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像不怎麼吃驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來就覺得她是個奇怪的傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 考慮到她靠近你的那個時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然對於她是誰的式神這一點我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,結果 至始至終都是謎一般的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,冬兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我呢 想去東京
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,式神必須隨時待在主人身邊才對的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,請盡快進入陰陽塾就讀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是因為土御門家的威望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,還是因為鈴鹿事件的功勞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 隨便什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,能成為夏目的力量的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呆虎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呆虎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,遭了 幻象?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也稍微…不曉得該如何下定決心…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.20,0:20:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,夏目?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.27,0:20:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,幹什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,當然是來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼用那種男人般的說話方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.67,0:20:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,還有打扮也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這是本家的「家規」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,「身為土御門家的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在外言行舉止須如男子」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,課是沒有問題 應該說是「家規」那方面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 那個時候說的是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,總之 原因就是這樣 所以你要配合我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再次請你多多指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了? 再次?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,難道真的全部明白了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 全部明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 我騙了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,還一直把你蒙在鼓裡 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,太誇張了吧 又不是被你騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,難道沒有發現嗎 剛才說「全部都明白了」是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是說 穿男裝是「家規」這事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不明白 你這個騙子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼總是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你們倆個我真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.62,0:21:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,冬兒 事情已經辦完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 只是去打個招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.78,0:21:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,之前和你提起的 我的青梅竹馬夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼冬兒會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 為什麼你會知道冬兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.37,0:22:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 這傢伙也一起進入陰陽塾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,進陰陽塾什麼的 冬兒還是個外行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.65,0:22:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我本來就能「靈視」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,被捲入靈災時的後遺症
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,原本就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我很擅長分辨人和式神
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那個髮帶很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,春虎 呆虎這稱呼還真是很適合你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 在陰陽塾都是我的後輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.51,0:22:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,給我作好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.13,0:22:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.94,0:22:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊 冬兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,她平常不是那副模樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.07,0:22:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不…平時就一直都是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.21,0:23:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.83,0:23:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快點過來 呆虎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是是 我的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1147.17,322.5)\fs37.5\1c&H000000&\bord0}距離出場還有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.96,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1056.604,450)\fs37.5\1c&H000000&\bord0}1集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,終於下週春虎大人要進陰陽塾了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,「咻」的插進去再轉一轉
